         MACRO ,                                          ADDED GP08124
&NM      XECHO &OFF,&BUF=R10
         LCLC  &LOF
.*
.*    THIS MACRO CLEARS THE SCREEN AND ECHOES THE USER'S INPUT,
.*    PROVIDING A STANDARDIZED FORMAT FOR CORRECTING ERRORS.
.*
&LOF     SETC  '&OFF'
         AIF   ('&LOF' NE '').HAVEOFF
&LOF     SETC  '28'          STANDARD OFFSET FOR 'UNAVAILABLE' MSG
.HAVEOFF ANOP  ,
&NM      BAL   R14,BLANKER
         AIF   ('&BUF' EQ '').NOBUF
         L     &BUF,BUFAD
         MVC   &LOF.(L'REPLY,&BUF),REPLY  ECHO INPUT
.NOBUF   L     R5,REPPTR     AND PRIME SCANNING
         MEND  ,
